Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.10,0:01:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭即將開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.20,0:01:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學校充滿了熱鬧的氣氛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.91,0:01:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們1年D班自然也不例外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.91,0:01:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通過了衛生檢查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.78,0:01:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們「飯糰亭」得以順利開張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.42,0:01:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過為了慎重起見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.06,0:01:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再次徵詢有關飯糰材料的意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.59,0:01:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飯糰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.46,0:01:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像跟我挺有緣的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.83,0:02:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了！就做三色飯糰如何!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.20,0:02:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一個飯糰裡放三種材料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.30,0:02:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會很受歡迎的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.81,0:02:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊 很可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.54,0:02:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩同學 最好不要哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.35,0:02:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把鹹鮭魚子、蔥、味噌和梅干放在一起好不好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.85,0:02:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噁～噁心死了～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.49,0:02:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最噁心的是妳的個性吧…章魚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.29,0:02:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛把鐵管帶來學校啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.80,0:02:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆舉辦飯糰戰鬥吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.77,0:02:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.03,0:02:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1對1 沒有任何限制 一招分勝負！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.80,0:02:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像是噴血或是手脫臼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.64,0:02:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以飯糰為名的戰鬥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.97,0:02:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駁回！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.08,0:02:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…用「沒中」好不好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.11,0:02:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒中？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.55,0:02:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像是買三送一的方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.42,0:02:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過第四個放的很可能是特別的材料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.79,0:02:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是「沒中」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.76,0:02:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贊成！意見不錯哦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.49,0:03:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你們都聽他的意見!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.40,0:03:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有什麼聽不聽的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.43,0:03:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的意見太奇怪了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.03,0:03:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡奇怪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.67,0:03:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰會為了飯糰打得全身是血？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.90,0:03:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾啊 夾夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.24,0:03:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我夾夾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.04,0:03:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.71,0:03:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必須去出席幹部會議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.68,0:03:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有關材料的採買就麻煩大家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.62,0:03:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.12,0:03:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊、等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.19,0:03:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有件事情想請教你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.02,0:03:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.26,0:03:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希～有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.83,0:03:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希 由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.23,0:03:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希 由希～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.60,0:03:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.43,0:03:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 貓咪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.63,0:03:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候跑進來的？哪裡來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.30,0:03:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道啊！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.31,0:03:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦！那隻貓是怎麼搞的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.65,0:03:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.68,0:03:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 妳的舉動才奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.62,0:03:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 那傢伙的個性還真差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.75,0:04:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這還用說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.12,0:04:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟王子剛好相反…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.63,0:04:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.63,0:04:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.10,0:04:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾真的很喜歡高的地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.31,0:04:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你每次都突然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.21,0:04:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊 小貓咪 好可愛哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.85,0:04:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很有貓咪緣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.82,0:04:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道啊 是它自己靠過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.02,0:04:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戌是狗 子是老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好高興哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興妳個頭啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.56,0:04:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前和樂羅在山上散步的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.69,0:04:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被幾十隻豬包圍 還以為會被吃掉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.00,0:04:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.30,0:04:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.67,0:04:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.44,0:04:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 只是有點擔心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.97,0:04:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很生氣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.11,0:04:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不打算參加文化祭的準備嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒去有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.08,0:05:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有由希在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切就搞定了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.09,0:05:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家只信賴他一個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.09,0:05:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從以前就是這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.56,0:05:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的頭腦又好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.10,0:05:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又會掌握要領 人緣也很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.97,0:05:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身旁的人都會自然地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.33,0:05:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認同他的才能而尊敬他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.27,0:05:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就拿學武來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.24,0:05:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先學的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.98,0:05:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是現在卻是他比較強…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.71,0:05:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.41,0:05:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鼠年生的小孩真的比較「特別」呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.92,0:05:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 真「特別」…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.65,0:05:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起來貓年的小孩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.29,0:05:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貓年的小孩就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.69,0:05:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貓年的小孩就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.09,0:05:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽了就不爽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.52,0:05:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要把那傢伙比下去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.56,0:05:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.90,0:05:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為阿夾他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.27,0:05:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那種容易和人相處的類型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.44,0:06:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於他是不屬於十二生肖的自然體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.98,0:06:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此能很自然地和「普通」人相處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.28,0:06:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想像他一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.39,0:06:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然…草摩同學羨慕阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.33,0:06:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而夾反而羨慕草摩同學…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.73,0:06:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為互相羨慕 反而處不來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.61,0:06:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.88,0:06:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼人都要羨慕別人呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.09,0:06:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼都不會發覺自己的優點呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.50,0:06:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有飯糰店的味道囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.74,0:07:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊、早安 你每天都這麼早呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.94,0:07:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 很平常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾 那是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.68,0:07:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韭菜飯糰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.18,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳幹嘛做這種東西！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.41,0:07:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…這是有關文化祭沒中的飯糰所做的研究
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.92,0:07:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有什麼好的建議呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.36,0:07:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飯糰上面放鮭魚或是鱈魚卵不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.42,0:07:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我自己做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.03,0:07:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾 你好棒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.00,0:07:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你捏飯糰的手法好厲害哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.20,0:07:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了！真令人意外呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.44,0:07:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修行期間都是我自己做飯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.74,0:07:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是手法熟練跟好吃是不一樣的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.44,0:07:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…要是讓潛心修行做壽司的人看到的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.85,0:07:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會很羨慕你那種熟練的捏飯糰技巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.12,0:07:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰會做那種修行啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.22,0:07:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 怎麼會有這種奇怪的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.86,0:08:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厲害的話就是厲害…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.83,0:08:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你自己沒有察覺呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.50,0:08:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許是黏在你的背上呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.91,0:08:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.34,0:08:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.28,0:08:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,例如每個人的優點 就像是飯糰的梅干一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.38,0:08:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個梅干就黏在背上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.99,0:08:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個世上每個人的背上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.55,0:08:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都黏了各種形狀、各種口味的梅干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.39,0:08:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是因為黏在背上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.59,0:08:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以無法知道這些梅干的好處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.73,0:08:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得自己一無是處…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.83,0:08:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是一堆白米而已…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.87,0:08:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實根本不是這麼一回事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.94,0:08:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背上就黏著梅干呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.21,0:08:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之所以會羨慕別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.12,0:09:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為看到別人背上的梅干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.82,0:09:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了 我確實看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.29,0:09:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾背上有…了不起的梅干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.03,0:09:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩同學很棒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.63,0:09:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾你也很棒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.37,0:09:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道妳怎麼會有這種鬼想法！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.07,0:09:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會用梅干來比喻我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.21,0:09:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真、真是抱歉 那用鮭魚來比喻好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.61,0:09:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思 都怪我胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.32,0:09:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.15,0:09:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.02,0:09:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的背上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.25,0:09:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也黏著梅干哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.70,0:09:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.67,0:09:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過是很小的梅干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.91,0:09:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小梅干很好吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常～非常～小的梅干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.08,0:10:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的！或許現在就有人羨慕我呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.85,0:10:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羨慕我自己沒有注意到的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.32,0:10:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要這麼想的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.92,0:10:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會想要一點一點的努力看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.40,0:10:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭當天來臨囉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.34,0:10:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這個台子歪歪的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.77,0:10:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別注意這麼細微的事啦 貓癡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.21,0:10:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對嘛 貓癡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.74,0:10:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要沒壞就行了嘛 貓癡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.68,0:10:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你們一直貓癡貓癡的叫個不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.45,0:10:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我當傻瓜嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.62,0:10:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.85,0:10:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你嘴巴很壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.92,0:10:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你是個很喜歡動物的好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.62,0:10:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.62,0:10:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對個頭啦！你們這些傢伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.49,0:10:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都對他改觀了 真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.23,0:10:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一回來就吵吵鬧鬧 真是吵的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.43,0:10:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…沒想到他會那麼坦率的回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.33,0:10:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是難得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.74,0:10:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩同學是草摩同學 阿夾是阿夾嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.28,0:11:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由‧希～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.85,0:11:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.45,0:11:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我們有禮物要送給你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學園祭的時候希望你一定要穿這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.95,0:11:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我們合買的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.82,0:11:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.93,0:11:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別為由希訂做的哦～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.34,0:11:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.08,0:11:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,味道如何呀～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.58,0:11:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.85,0:11:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇～賣得很好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.75,0:11:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好是飲食攤位第一名哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.29,0:11:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為本田同學捏的飯糰好吃嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.92,0:11:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？才、才不是呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.26,0:11:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個貓飯糰也很可愛哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.30,0:11:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對班上生意最有貢獻的人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.80,0:12:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！不要亂拍照啦～～～！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.44,0:12:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希會不高興哦～～！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.44,0:12:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 他真的是…太可愛了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.64,0:12:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶 客人都是衝著草摩同學來的呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.08,0:12:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我是不是做了什麼事惹草摩同學不高興…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.29,0:12:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別理他啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.32,0:12:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被迫穿女裝 惱羞成怒而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.73,0:12:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙對自己的女生相非常排斥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.53,0:12:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.97,0:12:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希 你好像女孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.07,0:12:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.07,0:12:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙為什麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.61,0:12:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？阿夾 你認識他嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.21,0:12:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別一個人到處轉來轉去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.68,0:12:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希和阿夾都很有朝氣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.02,0:12:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希的朋友耶～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.59,0:12:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.49,0:12:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帥呆了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.96,0:12:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 我是草摩紅葉 這位是草摩波鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.29,0:13:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是由希和阿夾的親戚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.56,0:13:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.27,0:13:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 紅葉就算了 為什麼連波鳥這傢伙都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.30,0:13:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 莫非這兩個人也是十二生肖…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.41,0:13:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 用力地深呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.74,0:13:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥是醫生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.11,0:13:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.75,0:13:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用不著在這裡診療吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.65,0:13:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經約好一個月要檢診一次的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,檢診？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.59,0:13:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩同學 你有哪裡不舒服嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.42,0:13:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…啊 沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.26,0:13:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希的氣管不太好 小時候經常發作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.36,0:13:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然長大之後變得健壯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.40,0:13:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過為了慎重起見還是要檢查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.44,0:13:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是本田透嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.24,0:13:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 請多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.97,0:13:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此…真的是個普通女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.31,0:13:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.31,0:13:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.31,0:13:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦！不能爬到台子上！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.18,0:13:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼啊！ 笨蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.35,0:13:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不、不好了 我失陪一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.45,0:14:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們來做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.16,0:14:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要抱怨去對慊人說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.16,0:14:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慊人知道有文化祭很想過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.36,0:14:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.50,0:14:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過他發燒到39度 被醫生攔了下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.07,0:14:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才會代替他來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.14,0:14:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而紅葉也跟著過來湊熱鬧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.34,0:14:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個都是湊熱鬧的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.98,0:14:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的要湊熱鬧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.95,0:14:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不會選在人比較少的傍晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.58,0:14:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 我們不是來對本田透下手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.15,0:14:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不那麼做是慊人下的決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.49,0:14:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡看什麼！\N嗚啊～～阿夾打我～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.70,0:14:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.66,0:14:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.43,0:14:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是小透吧 本田透！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.93,0:14:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.33,0:14:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是、我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.40,0:14:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉…是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.57,0:14:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 妳已經記得我的名字啦？好高興哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.54,0:14:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 以後請多多指教哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.91,0:14:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.21,0:15:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 小透 妳知道十二生肖的事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.45,0:15:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.25,0:15:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 那我可以盡情的抱妳嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.08,0:15:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！小色鬼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.39,0:15:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在小透面前變身應該沒關係吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也看場合吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.39,0:15:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他果然也是十二生肖之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.83,0:15:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是看小透可愛打算一個人獨占是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.83,0:15:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾 你是不是每天都抱著她？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.20,0:15:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！誰、誰做哪種事啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.23,0:15:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有機可乘！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.00,0:15:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.70,0:15:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.44,0:15:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.74,0:15:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那隻兔子是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.64,0:15:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.81,0:15:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是紅葉的衣服嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.38,0:15:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧！發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.48,0:15:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.75,0:15:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼紅葉會把衣服扔在這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.35,0:15:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有兔子…哪裡冒出來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了！妳說說話呀 本田同學！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.75,0:15:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來我才奇怪呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男生還做這種打扮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.89,0:15:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亂講 你是最棒的！草摩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.39,0:15:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的是女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.46,0:15:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會把你讓給別人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.16,0:15:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 很適合你呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從哪個角度看都是女生嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.90,0:15:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要有自信！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.90,0:15:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 草摩同學！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.47,0:15:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲自己來引起別人注意！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.04,0:16:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個死小孩 看看自己幹的好事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.64,0:16:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禁足一個星期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.41,0:16:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是、可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.11,0:16:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個好可怕～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.01,0:16:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少在那邊跟女孩子撒嬌～～！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.95,0:16:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 還好這次多虧了由希轉移了他們的注意力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.15,0:16:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼！賣弄風騷本來就是他的興趣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.36,0:16:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想飛得更高一點嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.66,0:16:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死老鼠…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.13,0:16:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉…你要多留神才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.23,0:16:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個愛惹事的小鬼 差不多該回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.30,0:16:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要回去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家還想跟小透說話呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.57,0:16:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用不著那麼趕啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.44,0:16:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引起騷動就要馬上回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.71,0:16:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是事先說好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.65,0:16:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥真是無趣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.38,0:16:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕快滾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.22,0:16:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…忘記一件重要的事了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.42,0:16:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希 夾 你們站在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.66,0:16:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡潔地回答我的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.33,0:16:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1加1等於多少？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.43,0:16:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.30,0:17:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慊人要我幫你們兩個照張相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.34,0:17:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍了一張不錯的合照！再見了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.97,0:17:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.51,0:17:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥～～～等一下～～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.21,0:17:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是沒弄清楚波鳥的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.25,0:17:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是不是十二生肖之一呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.88,0:17:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是這副模樣的相片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.62,0:17:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被慊人看到了 不曉得他會怎麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.59,0:17:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩同學 你會感冒的！你的氣管…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.73,0:17:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了這副模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.03,0:17:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是大家都很喜歡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.63,0:17:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男生被說可愛有什麼值得高興的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.24,0:17:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思…我也覺得很可愛呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.84,0:17:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.08,0:17:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想讓妳看到我這副醜態…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.55,0:17:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像個白癡似的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.82,0:17:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然應該拒絕她們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.82,0:18:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 媽媽說我很可愛的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.80,0:18:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得很高興呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.00,0:18:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 好可愛喲～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.60,0:18:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常非常高興…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.61,0:18:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…愛情的表現…雖然媽媽她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.61,0:18:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再也不會這樣說我了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.38,0:18:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以這也意味著大家在說「喜歡你」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.42,0:18:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…這個…沒有什麼其它的含意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.99,0:18:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.50,0:18:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽妳說我可愛居然有種高興的感覺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.10,0:18:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.53,0:18:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了學姊她們 再奉送一段時間好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.14,0:18:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 妳能先幫我拿下來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.41,0:18:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮被鈕扣鉤住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.65,0:18:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這套洋裝穿和脫都很麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.72,0:18:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是妳來穿的話一定很適合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.12,0:19:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.36,0:19:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也很嚮往呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像公主一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.69,0:19:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.69,0:19:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.40,0:19:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是妳穿的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定很可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.32,0:19:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相機搶過來了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.32,0:19:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少囉唆 根本沒機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.35,0:19:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本田同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.35,0:19:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於波鳥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.83,0:19:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有機會見到他的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好避免和他獨處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.96,0:19:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.33,0:19:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…並不是波鳥本身有什麼不好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.34,0:19:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳說過我以前洩漏真面目的事吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.27,0:19:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時把所有人的記憶消除的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.65,0:20:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是波鳥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.28,0:20:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我有些擔心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須先提醒妳才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.46,0:20:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1年D班本田透同學 1年D班本田透同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.26,0:20:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請立即到一樓諮詢室來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.90,0:20:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重復一次 1年D班本田…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.40,0:20:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在叫我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.13,0:20:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.87,0:20:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先去看看再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.87,0:20:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.11,0:20:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把妳找過來 真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.14,0:20:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾就不用說了 要是由希在場的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.98,0:20:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無法好好跟妳說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.48,0:20:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在只有我們兩個獨處！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.52,0:20:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點冒昧 不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.25,0:20:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次放假的時候到草摩本家來玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.56,0:20:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.29,0:20:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有些事情想告訴妳 很重要的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.60,0:20:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然 不能對由希他們說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.40,0:20:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒有權利拒絕 妳明白我的意思嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.21,0:21:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該、該怎麼辦才好呢…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.74,0:21:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是拒絕的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.98,0:21:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的記憶就會被消除吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.61,0:21:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可、可是…或許真的是很重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.75,0:21:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說不能隨便懷疑別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.45,0:21:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.75,0:21:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.19,0:21:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥不會侵犯妳的啦 我會在旁邊守護妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.43,0:21:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定要來哦 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.03,0:21:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.06,0:21:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.43,0:21:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透是女孩子耶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.90,0:21:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟兩個男生單獨相處會害怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.23,0:21:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小透 要來哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.84,0:21:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉要我去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.11,0:21:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就放心多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.34,0:21:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥突然要我到本家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.32,0:21:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還要瞞著紫吳、草摩同學和阿夾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.89,0:21:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟有什麼事要對我說呢…
